comment: Safari Rally Kenya is a demanding one. Let's see after Saturday. I would say this day will tell us a lot.
Similar stages to the previous two years, but different conditions. A bit more rough from what we have some seen in recce. I need some Kenyan gods this weekend to help me. Luck will be needed!
